{"tid":785803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"猶太人同中國人做生意分別","createTime":"2018-08-19T13:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T15:26:00.000Z","uid":66943,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"43d5fd04e5847a1be79f8a08fc75d361cac00ea7","tid":785803,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:20:31.000Z","msg":"Think different, do different.「如果不能做得更好，就做得不同」<br />\n<br />\n第一個猶太人來到小鎮上開了個加油站，生意很旺。<br />\n<br />\n第二個猶太人來了，發現加油站生意很不錯，想到加油站的客戶需要吃飯，所以投資開了個餐館。<br />\n<br />\n第三個猶太人來了，想到來小鎮的人多了需要住宿，於是開了個酒店。<br />\n<br />\n第四個猶太人又發現住店的人需要生活用品，於是開了超市。<br />\n<br />\n第五個，第六個&hellip;&hellip;來的人越來越多，吃飯住宿旅遊經商的人又需要加油，於是加油站、餐館、飯店、超市的生意相繼更旺了，逐步小鎮就成了一個經濟繁榮的小鎮，很多猶太人都富裕了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一個中國人來到小鎮上開了個加油站，生意很旺。<br />\n<br />\n第二個中國人來了，發現第一個人投資的加油站生意真令人羨慕，趕緊開了第二個加油站。<br />\n<br />\n第三個中國人又來了，看見前面2個同胞的加油站生意很好妒嫉得眼紅，火速開了第三個加油站。<br />\n<br />\n第四，第五個同胞過來都是一樣，開加油站還打折促銷&hellip;&hellip;最後惡性競爭，然後紛紛倒閉，小鎮又回到原點&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/211635_bf8d5d9a09527df6d9f0e2540aa95214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F211635_bf8d5d9a09527df6d9f0e2540aa95214.jpg&h=4d32c038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成功，不在於你贏過多少人，而在於你與多少人分享利益，幫過多少人。你與之分享的人越多，幫過的人愈多，服務的地方愈廣，那你成功的機會就愈大。<br />\n<br />\n睇到759又諗返起le篇野"},{"pid":"ac06739920925e9ae2774be6351d440a8495eff7","tid":785803,"uid":59163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"所以話全世界都憎支那人唔係冇原因"},{"pid":"0045a546e1e5d75f75ee3212287f0204b9c09890","tid":785803,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"中國人果d叫on9"},{"pid":"6ee7482d6b3667ea90ce031f3b74f7ab26ba4308","tid":785803,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"講做生意，冇技術壟斷下全世界都唔夠大陸佬黎，同行為左競爭咩賤招都會出齊。"},{"pid":"9a855efa19345d7e926be4dd00f055451b5ac454","tid":785803,"uid":91931,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/013619_f2efff185315a0995c5ac3051c139014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F013619_f2efff185315a0995c5ac3051c139014.jpg&h=81155296&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73fea8b371fcc722ae1301a32ce1c225659f48af","tid":785803,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:49:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd661f4467cc95ec8664ef9f624d194ecd40ba63","tid":785803,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"但中國人賺左錢再開各行各業<br />\n變左你冇得唔幫襯佢"},{"pid":"4ac8f965d82354c219b8b9862576f25de7e5bcd3","tid":785803,"uid":155732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd661f4467cc95ec8664ef9f624d194ecd40ba63","tid":785803,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"但中國人賺左錢再開各行各業<br />\n變左你冇得唔幫襯佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"韓國一樣<br />\nsamsung<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5e88d238334beee549285273179cad1d1052c1","tid":785803,"uid":77458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"睇做咩生意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時候同類型店開埋一齊都有好處嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4e027257b52c324d5cb2eed536d80983118b8b","tid":785803,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"華人社會班有錢人一賺到錢就會做好多野阻其他人搵錢機會 因為咁可以幫佢地製造更多奴隸"},{"pid":"b9ae3aeb7a984d508145156edfd1436f297aa953","tid":785803,"uid":57513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"73fea8b371fcc722ae1301a32ce1c225659f48af","tid":785803,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:49:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"細心d睇其實有好多唔同類型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6463668c4d2843c9f2e14061ff8ecf0924c195c8","tid":785803,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9ae3aeb7a984d508145156edfd1436f297aa953","tid":785803,"uid":57513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"73fea8b371fcc722ae1301a32ce1c225659f48af","tid":785803,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:49:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"細心d睇其實有好多唔同類型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"底板買賣、各種軟件硬件交易<br />\n雖然表面上都係電腦野<br />\n但個個都做緊唔同嘅野"},{"pid":"583598a167da366b8feb5af8236953f6c9ba69c0","tid":785803,"uid":198720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73fea8b371fcc722ae1301a32ce1c225659f48af","tid":785803,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:49:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:43:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔可以攞黎做例子<br />\n<br />\n全香港好似黃金高登賣電腦野做得咁大其實無乜<br />\n<br />\n好似我咁我要砌機我都坐車出深水埗<br />\n<br />\n因為自己將軍澳果啲無可能信得過  9唔搭八"},{"pid":"7177662508d02ad2495e90ed20c7d159c521fdb2","tid":785803,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"西方人同中國人嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n中國人中意睇埋樓主呢類content farm 9up文，不經思考仲信到十足十，所以思考力低，解釋唔到任何經濟現象<br />\n<br />\n西方人見到呢d文會屌都廢事，其實樓上都有提到類似例子，高登黃金，仲有影印舖,波鞋街,lkf呢d，其實呢個係一個好typical嘅經濟學現象，稍為對經濟有認識嘅人都唔會用咩「中國人頂爛市」黎解釋呢d現象，因為絕對唔係中國獨有，所以經濟學源自西方，唔係源自中國<br />\n<br />\n由此po可見，大部份連登仔都係個d唔撚用腦中意信埋d content farm嘅中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13284af8bc3bf7060cd28fcea4bf935a4a927a79","tid":785803,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:16:03.000Z","msg":"規模經濟效應，簡稱聚集經濟，又稱為聚集經濟效應，群聚效應，是一個建立在規模經濟和網絡外部性間的學說。這個詞是用來形容在一個地區之上，許多相同抑或不同類型的產業聚集後，會因為空間上的集中而獲得好處。<br />\n<br />\n例如：工業區設立後，各種產業共用公共設施，節省成本。汽車生產工廠設於某地後，相關零組件廠商設於該工廠旁，以降低運輸成本及時間。矽谷電腦產業，底特律汽車產業，日本歌舞妓仃，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港的波鞋街</span>，旺角花墟等等。"},{"pid":"2d5a0988cafc36881096c97802346f6cfd0e6117","tid":785803,"uid":85410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:22:47.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪講緊依家果啲奶茶店現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e393b7778b2b55786c1c5fbcc33f9219da3256ec","tid":785803,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"成街都係垃圾珍珠奶茶"},{"pid":"39296a0da66b87378fa1a9980901ea4b2b66e9f4","tid":785803,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"篇嘢有冇20年"}]}